    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows clear signs of its age and regular use. While the engine and transmission remain functional for daily driving, you will notice some cosmetic wear on the exterior, including several noticeable scratches and minor dings. The interior also shows signs of wear, particularly on the driver's seat and floor mats. Mechanically, the car is reliable for commuting, though it may require more frequent maintenance than a newer model. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a more accessible price point.",
      "price": 24200.0,
