    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking dependable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s been a trusty companion and is eager to get back out there!",
